room_title: Escape room "The Study" by Escape Manor in Panama City
room_description:
A wedding couple madly in love was to be wedded, however, a draft caused the groom to be whisked away to war before he could marry his bride to be. Upon return from the war, his bride has disappeared. He has spent many years tracking her down and after claiming to have found her, the groom disappears.
We are giving you access to the Study for one hour to see if you can solve the mystery of what happened to him and his bride. Will you solve the mystery? Will you escape?
